title: Jewish Learning with Rabbi Wolpe
desc: Being Jewish is tough. It's expensive, it's tiring, and frankly, there are a million bazillion rules. But fear not! Rabbi David Wolpe, in a 3 part lecture series is going to explain to our young professional community why you should be Jewish! November 12th: Why Be Jewish? December 17th: Why Marry Jewish? February 18th: Why Faith Matters $10 per session $18 when you buy all three Free for members, email edusedau@sinaitemple.org for your discount code.
